intro: The following is a list of all the commands you can use with the bot.

accordion.desc: Accordion is used for showing and hiding content but only one item can stay open at a time.

alert.desc: Alert informs users about important events.

avatar.desc: Avatars are used to show a thumbnail representation of an individual or business in the interface.

badge.desc: Badges are used to inform the user of the status of specific data.

breadcrumb.desc: Breadcrumbs helps users to navigate through the website.

button.desc: Buttons allow the user to take actions or make choices.

dropdown.desc: Dropdown can open a menu or any other element when the button is clicked.
